<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>
    Welcome <%-name%>
  </title>

  <%- include('../styles-global.ejs') %>
    <%- include('./styles-welcome-exhibitor.ejs') %>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="root-wrapper mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-sm">Well done,<span class="mr-1 blue-1 font-semibold">
        <%-name%>
      </span>
    </h1>
    <div class="blue-2 text-lg font-bold">Your account has been created successfully!</div>

    <div class="mt-10">
      <p>
        Now the institution can benefit from the platform's innovative features such as digital marketing, selling its
        products and/or services quickly and safely.
      </p>

      <div class="my-10">
        <p>
          However, for security reasons and the best possible optimization of our services, it is necessary that this
          email be confirmed.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>
        To do so, click on the button below and follow the subsequent steps.
      </p>

      <div class="mx-auto my-10 w-max block">
        <div class="mx-auto w-max">
          <a target="_blank"
            href="http://accounts.fikani.com/confirm-email?utm_email=<%-email%>&utm_type=exhibitor&utm_key=<%-key%>">
            <button class="btn mt-2 white-1 bg-blue-1 rounded-lg py-3 px-6 uppercase text-md font-bold">
              Confirm email and login
            </button>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 my-6 text-sm">
        <p>In case you need further assistance, write to us on</p>
        <a class="text-[#387ebf]" href="mailto:support@fikani.com">support@fikani.com</a>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm">Thank you, <span class="font-semibold">FIKANI Digital</span>.</div>


    </div>
  </div>

</body>

</html>